                    "comment": "Gained an understanding of how this component works by looking at existing unittests. I wrote several tests that demonstrate surprising behavior.\r\n\r\nFor example, if you pass a NotEmpty validator to Zend_Filter_Input, with a custom message preset in the validator object, this message will show if you validate using the validator directly. However, if you use the same instance inside Zend_Filter_Input, the default message shows.\r\n\r\nIf you pass in a custom message in the same array as where you pass the validator, then the custom message is used.",
